---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About | Zemi">
    <main class="container">
        <h1>About me</h1>

        <div class="terminal-box">
            <p><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami</p>
            <p><strong>[HANDLE]:</strong> Zemi</p>
            <p><strong>[STATUS]:</strong> Active</p>
            <p><strong>[SPECIALTY]:</strong> Pwn, Crypto, Rev</p>
            <p><strong>[MOTTO]:</strong> "I don't know the flag, but I will find it."</p>
        </div>

        <section class="prose">
            <p>
                I go by <strong>Zemi</strong> online. I play CTFs whenever I can, mostly pwn, crypto, and rev. That's where I'm most comfortable, but I'll throw myself at other categories too if nothing else is clicking.
            </p>
            <p>
                Most of my stuff is written in Python and C. I got into this through curiosity more than anything, wanted to understand how things actually worked under the hood. Breaking them turned out to be the fastest way to learn.
            </p>
            <p>
                When I'm not staring at a disassembler I'm probably reading write-ups from people way better than me or messing with some new tool I found.
            </p>

            <h2>Find me</h2>
            <p>
                My <a href={`${base}/blog`}>challenge write-ups</a> are on here, and my scripts and random projects live on <a href="https://github.com/imattas" target="_blank">GitHub</a>. Feel free to poke around.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .terminal-box {
        background-color: #161b22;
        border: 1px solid #30363d;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .terminal-box p {
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        color: #e6edf3;
    }

    .prompt {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .prose h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: var(--text-heading);
    }

    .roster-list {
        list-style-type: square;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .roster-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }
</style>
